{"tid":1454416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"溫故知新：國泰航空空中霸王遭擊落事故","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:11:39.000Z","uid":255105,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4fd7ee919f559921fa80201c197712e7c2c48aea","tid":1454416,"uid":255105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"國泰空中霸王被擊落事故發生於1954年7月23日，國泰航空1架DC-4「空中霸王」客機（Skymaster），自泰國曼谷飛回香港途中，在中華人民共和國海南島三亞以東的南海上空<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">遭2架中國人民解放軍空軍La-11戰鬥機擊落</span></strong>。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">造成10死8傷</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n事發經過：<br />\n1954年7月23日早上（2019GMT，香港時間0419），機身編號VR-HEU的國泰DC-4型客機，載著6名機組人員及12名乘客[2] 從曼谷返港。此班機原由新加坡起飛，停曼谷後繼續返港。早上0840（香港時間），飛機以9000英呎高度，飛至海南島以東30海浬之南海上空，位於國際航線之內。[4] 機長及副機長發現飛機兩側分別各出現一架螺旋槳戰機[4]（中方資料稱為解放軍空29師所屬）[5]。發現戰機後不久，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">飛機在毫無預警的情況下遭解放軍戰機射擊</span></strong>。一號、四號引擎及油箱被擊中及即時起火，火勢向機體四處蔓延。[4]機長認為是被拉-9戰鬥機0.50英寸（12.7毫米）機槍攻擊 。<br />\n<br />\n7月26日，中華人民共和國外交部對英方表示遺憾，指出7月23日事件起因是兩架戰機當時在三亞榆林港南部海域上空執行為蘇聯東歐國家輪船護航巡邏任務時[註 1]發現了一架大型飛機，地面指揮命令查明，但兩名戰機飛行員誤以為飛機是屬於中華民國空軍的轟炸機，並擅自將其擊落。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國指事件屬於意外</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，對傷者及受難者家屬致以同情及慰問，並表示將向相關方面負擔賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日放氧氣，明日出子彈</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9fe69416447943ddd6df01e0b30d374750a3bd86","tid":1454416,"uid":255105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD%E9%9C%B8%E7%8E%8B%E9%81%AD%E6%93%8A%E8%90%BD%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%259C%25B8%25E7%258E%258B%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%2590%25BD%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2595%2585&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ6g2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=c98670e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD%E9%9C%B8%E7%8E%8B%E9%81%AD%E6%93%8A%E8%90%BD%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85</a>"},{"pid":"0b68f99f04d725296a88de1577c74ff2531200e7","tid":1454416,"uid":255105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:20:15.000Z","msg":"大家搭飛機可能好快就會死於意外啦，小心睇路"},{"pid":"0ff24c8206c3d2a729bf3833e43b3c49dbeec55e","tid":1454416,"uid":40826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:22:31.000Z","msg":"屌 每次諗返起都好撚嬲 中國幾時先可以滅國"},{"pid":"3a2fb4100e2808e011144019d3fc1f872228f8e7","tid":1454416,"uid":271407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d81ff59a75deeabc8046d96efa714fc8eef9b0","tid":1454416,"uid":91519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"推俾航空業界知"},{"pid":"64a974d6190c54828cefbc4606a8102719870b3d","tid":1454416,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:11:39.000Z","msg":"而家先知有咁既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}